This lecture is about using spring boot actuator:

To use the actuator endpoints
    1-Adding maven xml of to pom.xml file:
    <dependency>
    			<groupId>org.springframework.boot</groupId>
    			<artifactId>spring-boot-starter-actuator</artifactId>
    </dependency>

    2- By default actuator/health exposed
    3- To enable other actuators check the lecture 19 and application.properties file

    4- Info endpoints return empty JSON object by default, so you need to customize the return data in application.properties
